                            <comment id="12499603" author="knutanders" created="Mon, 28 May 2007 16:22:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The attached patch reduces the time required to run SecureServerTest on my machine from 5 minutes 8 seconds to about 8 seconds. It makes pingForServerStart() check the status of the server process and stop pinging it if it&apos;s dead. I&apos;m running suites.All with it now.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
